 historial de toda la conversaci\u00f3n que vamos a tener y acceder a tu actividad en el sitio web durante la conversaci\u00f3n."},"livechat.conversations.consent.legal.otherInformation":{"en":"","es":""},"livechat.conversations.consent.legal.purposes":{"en":"We collect and process your data because you gave us your express consent.\r\nPurpose: We collect and keep records of chats so we can provide you the best possible support and enhance our products and services.","es":"Recopilamos y tratamos sus datos bajo su consentimiento expreso. \r\nFinalidad: Recopilamos y registramos los chats para poder ofrecerle el mejor apoyo posible y mejorar nuestros productos y servicios."},"livechat.conversations.consent.legal.recipients":{"en":"You may introduce a claim with the data protection authority of your country to protecciondedatos@nh-hotels.com or you can contact our DPO at dpo@nh-hotels.com","es":"Puede realizar una solicitud a trav\u00e9s del email protecciondedatos@nh-hotels.com o contactar con nuestro DPO en dpo@nh-hotels.com."},"livechat.conversations.consent.legal.yourRights":{"en":"Unconditional rights\r\nAt any time, you may:\r\n * Rectify your personal data\r\n * Obtain a copy of such personal data\r\n\r\nConditional rights\r\nAs the case may be, you may:\r\n * Withdraw your consent where one of our use is based hereupon\r\n * Request the transfer to anyone of data we hold on the basis of your consent\r\n * Request that we keep your data without using it in case of inaccuracy, unlawfulness, while we examine your refusal that we use your data or should you need if before courts\r\n * Request deletion in case data is unnecessary or where you have withdrawn consent \r\n \r\n","es":"Derechos incondicionales\r\nCuando quiera, puede:\r\n * Corregir sus datos personales\r\n * Obtener una copia de esos datos personales\r\n\r\nDerechos condicionales\r\nSi procede, puede:\r\n * Retirar su consentimiento para alguno de los usos aqu\u00ed indicados.\r\n * Solicitar la cesi\u00f3n de los datos que guardamos bajo su autorizaci\u00f3n.\r\n * Solicitar que guardemos sus datos sin hacer uso de ellos en caso de imprecisi\u00f3n o ilegalidad mientras examinamos su rechazo a que utilicemos sus datos o si lo necesita ante los tribunales.\r\n * Solicitar la eliminaci\u00f3n si los datos son innecesarios o donde haya retirado su consentimiento.\r\n"}},"proactifData":[{"id":283641,"campaignId":"3016cd16-316d-4d20-936b-19f76232e701","campaignName":"NH Hotels - main strategy","type":"interaction","label":"BFL - ES - Desktop - Test IDZ ","channel":"chat","skill":null,"targetingConditions":[{"logicalOperator":"contains","value":"nh","criteria":{"id":"targeting_condition_criteria.PAGE_EN_COURS","type":"STRING","field":"actualScreen"},"targetingConditionCriteria":{"id":"targeting_condition_criteria.PAGE_EN_COURS","type":"STRING","field":"actualScreen"},"visitorAttribute":null},{"logicalOperator":"notIs","value":"mobile","criteria":{"id":"targeting_condition_criteria.DEVICE_TYPE","type":"DEVICE","field":"deviceType"},"targetingConditionCriteria":{"id":"targeting_condition_criteria.DEVICE_TYPE","type":"DEVICE","field":"deviceType"},"visitorAttribute":null},{"logicalOperator":"contains","value":"?idz","criteria":{"id":"targeting_condition_criteria.PAGE_EN_COURS","type":"STRING","field":"actualScreen"},"targetingConditionCriteria":{"id":"targeting_condition_criteria.PAGE_EN_COURS","type":"STRING","field":"actualScreen"},"visitorAttribute":null}],"targetingActions":[{"type":"button","data":{"id":"23731","button":{"id":"23731","width":"250","pos":"right","reduce":"0","type":"chat","on":"\/\/fstatic.iadvize.com\/images\/livechat\/nh-hotels\/idz-nh-hotels-btn-ibbu-es.png","mini":"\/\/fstatic.iadvize.com\/images\/livechat\/nh-hotels\/idz-nh-hotels-btn-reduit-es.png"}},"id":"0e5f2baa-106b-4a25-bd8a-0ce53115eaf5"}]},{"id":286574,"campaignId":"3016cd16-316d-4d20-936b-19f76232e701","campaignName":"NH Hotels - main strategy","type":"interaction","label":"BFL - ES - C